msgid "# Qwen-VL-Dense(Qwen3-VL-2B/4B/8B/32B)"
msgstr "# Qwen-VL-Dense（Qwen3-VL-2B/4B/8B/32B）"

msgid "## 1 Introduction"
msgstr "## 1 简介"

msgid ""
"The Qwen-VL(Vision-Language)series from Alibaba Cloud comprises a family of "
"powerful Large Vision-Language Models (LVLMs) designed for comprehensive "
"multimodal understanding. They accept images, text, and bounding boxes as "
"input, and output text and detection boxes, enabling advanced functions like"
" image detection, multi-modal dialogue, and multi-image reasoning."
msgstr ""
"阿里云推出的Qwen-VL（视觉-"
"语言）系列包含一系列强大的大型视觉语言模型（LVLM），专为全面的多模态理解而设计。它们接受图像、文本和边界框作为输入，并输出文本和检测框，从而实现图像检测、多模态对话和多图像推理等高级功能。"

msgid ""
"This document will show the main verification steps of the model, including "
"supported features, feature configuration, environment preparation, NPU "
"deployment, accuracy and performance evaluation."
msgstr "本文档将展示该模型的主要验证步骤，包括支持的特性、特性配置、环境准备、NPU部署、精度和性能评估。"

msgid ""
"This tutorial uses the vLLM-Ascend `v0.11.0rc3-a3` version for "
"demonstration, showcasing the `Qwen3-VL-8B-Instruct` model as an example for"
" single NPU and multi-NPU deployment."
msgstr ""
"本教程使用 vLLM-Ascend `v0.11.0rc3-a3` 版本进行演示，以 `Qwen3-VL-8B-Instruct` "
"模型为例，展示单NPU和多NPU部署。"

msgid "## 2 Supported Features"
msgstr "## 2 支持的特性"

msgid ""
"Refer to [Supported Features "
"List](../../user_guide/support_matrix/supported_models.md) to get the "
"model's supported feature matrix."
msgstr ""
"请参考[支持的特性列表](../../user_guide/support_matrix/supported_models.md)获取模型支持的特性矩阵。"

msgid ""
"Refer to [Feature Guide](../../user_guide/feature_guide/index.md) to get the"
" feature's configuration."
msgstr "请参考[特性指南](../../user_guide/feature_guide/index.md)获取特性的配置。"

msgid "## 3 Prerequisites"
msgstr "## 3 前提条件"

msgid "### 3.1 Model Weight"
msgstr "### 3.1 模型权重"

msgid ""
"Requires 1 card in 1 Atlas 800I A2 (64G × 8) node or 1 card in 1 Atlas 800 "
"A3 (64G × 16) node:"
msgstr "需要1个Atlas 800I A2（64G × 8）节点中的1张卡或1个Atlas 800 A3（64G × 16）节点中的1张卡："

msgid ""
"- `Qwen3-VL-2B-Instruct`: [Download model weight](https://modelscope.cn/models/Qwen/Qwen3-VL-2B-Instruct)\n"
"- `Qwen3-VL-4B-Instruct`: [Download model weight](https://modelscope.cn/models/Qwen/Qwen3-VL-4B-Instruct)\n"
"- `Qwen3-VL-8B-Instruct`: [Download model weight](https://modelscope.cn/models/Qwen/Qwen3-VL-8B-Instruct)"
msgstr ""
"- `Qwen3-VL-2B-Instruct`：[下载模型权重](https://modelscope.cn/models/Qwen/Qwen3-VL-2B-Instruct)\n"
"- `Qwen3-VL-4B-Instruct`：[下载模型权重](https://modelscope.cn/models/Qwen/Qwen3-VL-4B-Instruct)\n"
"- `Qwen3-VL-8B-Instruct`：[下载模型权重](https://modelscope.cn/models/Qwen/Qwen3-VL-8B-Instruct)"

msgid ""
"Requires 2 cards in 1 Atlas 800I A2 (64G × 8) node or 2 cards in 1 Atlas 800"
" A3 (64G × 16) node:"
msgstr "需要1个Atlas 800I A2（64G × 8）节点中的2张卡或1个Atlas 800 A3（64G × 16）节点中的2张卡："

msgid ""
"- `Qwen3-VL-32B-Instruct`: [Download model "
"weight](https://modelscope.cn/models/Qwen/Qwen3-VL-32B-Instruct)"
msgstr ""
"- "
"`Qwen3-VL-32B-Instruct`：[下载模型权重](https://modelscope.cn/models/Qwen/Qwen3-VL-32B-Instruct)"

msgid ""
"It is recommended to download the model weight to the shared directory of "
"multiple nodes, such as `/root/.cache/`."
msgstr "建议将模型权重下载到多节点的共享目录，例如 `/root/.cache/`。"

msgid "## 4 Installation"
msgstr "## 4 安装"

msgid "### 4.1 Docker Image Installation"
msgstr "### 4.1 Docker镜像安装"

msgid ""
"Select an image based on your machine type and start the docker image on "
"your node, refer to [using docker](../../installation.md#set-up-using-"
"docker)."
msgstr ""
"根据您的机器类型选择镜像，并在节点上启动docker镜像，请参考[使用docker](../../installation.md#set-up-"
"using-docker)。"

msgid "**A3 series:**"
msgstr "**A3系列：**"

msgid "Start the docker image on each node."
msgstr "在每个节点上启动docker镜像。"

msgid ""
"After starting the container, run the following command to verify the "
"installation:"
msgstr "启动容器后，运行以下命令验证安装："

msgid ""
"Expected result: The container is listed with status `Up`. You can also "
"verify the vllm-ascend version inside the container:"
msgstr "预期结果：容器被列出，状态为 `Up`。您还可以在容器内验证 vllm-ascend 版本："

msgid ""
"Expected result: The version information is displayed, matching the pulled "
"image version."
msgstr "预期结果：显示版本信息，与拉取的镜像版本匹配。"

msgid "### 4.2 Source Code Installation"
msgstr "### 4.2 源码安装"

msgid ""
"If you prefer not to use the Docker image, you can build from source. "
"Install vLLM from source first:"
msgstr "如果您不想使用Docker镜像，可以从源码构建。首先从源码安装vLLM："

msgid "1. Clone and install vLLM:"
msgstr "1. 克隆并安装vLLM："

msgid "2. Clone and install the vLLM-Ascend repository:"
msgstr "2. 克隆并安装vLLM-Ascend仓库："

msgid "**Installation Verification:**"
msgstr "**安装验证：**"

msgid ""
"Expected result: The version information for both packages is displayed, "
"confirming a successful installation."
msgstr "预期结果：显示两个包的版本信息，确认安装成功。"

msgid ""
"If deploying a multi-node environment, set up the environment on each node."
msgstr "如果部署多节点环境，请在每个节点上设置环境。"

msgid ""
"For more details, please refer to the [Installation "
"Guide](../../installation.md)."
msgstr "更多详情，请参考[安装指南](../../installation.md)。"

msgid "## 5 Online Service Deployment"
msgstr "## 5 在线服务部署"

msgid "### 5.1 Single-Node Online Deployment"
msgstr "### 5.1 单节点在线部署"

msgid "Run docker container to start the vLLM server on single-NPU:"
msgstr "运行docker容器以在单NPU上启动vLLM服务器："

msgid "Key Parameter Descriptions:"
msgstr "关键参数说明："

msgid ""
"- Add `--max_model_len` option to avoid ValueError that the "
"Qwen3-VL-8B-Instruct model's max seq len (256000) is larger than the maximum"
" number of tokens that can be stored in KV cache. This will differ with "
"different NPU series based on the on-chip memory size. Please modify the "
"value according to a suitable value for your NPU series."
msgstr ""
"- 添加 `--max_model_len` "
"选项以避免ValueError，即Qwen3-VL-8B-Instruct模型的最大序列长度（256000）大于KV缓存中可存储的最大token数。此值因不同NPU系列的片上内存大小而异。请根据您的NPU系列修改为合适的值。"

msgid "If your service start successfully, you can see the info shown below:"
msgstr "如果您的服务启动成功，您将看到如下信息："

msgid "## 6 Functional Verification"
msgstr "## 6 功能验证"

msgid ""
"Once your server is started, you can query the model with input prompts:"
msgstr "服务器启动后，您可以使用输入提示查询模型："

msgid "Expected Result:"
msgstr "预期结果："

msgid "The service returns HTTP 200 OK."
msgstr "服务返回HTTP 200 OK。"

msgid "## 7 Accuracy Evaluation"
msgstr "## 7 精度评估"

msgid "### Using Language Model Evaluation Harness"
msgstr "### 使用语言模型评估工具"

msgid ""
"The accuracy of some models is already within our CI monitoring scope, "
"including:"
msgstr "部分模型的精度已在我们的CI监控范围内，包括："

msgid "- `Qwen3-VL-8B-Instruct`"
msgstr "- `Qwen3-VL-8B-Instruct`"

msgid ""
"As an example, take the `mmmu_val` dataset as a test dataset, and run "
"accuracy evaluation of `Qwen3-VL-8B-Instruct` in offline mode."
msgstr "以 `mmmu_val` 数据集作为测试数据集为例，在离线模式下运行 `Qwen3-VL-8B-Instruct` 的精度评估。"

msgid ""
"1. Refer to [Using "
"lm_eval](../../developer_guide/evaluation/using_lm_eval.md) for more details"
" on `lm_eval` installation."
msgstr ""
"1. 请参考[使用lm_eval](../../developer_guide/evaluation/using_lm_eval.md)了解 "
"`lm_eval` 安装的更多详情。"

msgid "2. Run `lm_eval` to execute the accuracy evaluation."
msgstr "2. 运行 `lm_eval` 执行精度评估。"

msgid ""
"3. After execution, you can get the result, here is the result of "
"`Qwen3-VL-8B-Instruct` in `vllm-ascend:0.11.0rc3` for reference only."
msgstr ""
"3. 执行后，您将获得结果，以下是 `Qwen3-VL-8B-Instruct` 在 `vllm-ascend:0.11.0rc3` "
"中的结果，仅供参考。"

msgid ""
"|  Tasks  |Value |Stderr|\n"
"    |---------|---|-----|\n"
"    |mmmu_val |0.5389|0.0159|"
msgstr ""
"|  Tasks  |Value |Stderr|\n"
"    |---------|---|-----|\n"
"    |mmmu_val |0.5389|0.0159|"

msgid "## 8 Performance Evaluation"
msgstr "## 8 性能评估"

msgid "### Using vLLM Benchmark"
msgstr "### 使用vLLM基准测试"

msgid ""
"Refer to [vLLM Benchmark](https://docs.vllm.ai/en/latest/benchmarking/) for "
"more details."
msgstr "更多详情请参考[vLLM基准测试](https://docs.vllm.ai/en/latest/benchmarking/)。"

msgid "There are three `vllm bench` subcommands:"
msgstr "有三个 `vllm bench` 子命令："

msgid ""
"- `latency`: Benchmark the latency of a single batch of requests.\n"
"- `serve`: Benchmark the online serving throughput.\n"
"- `throughput`: Benchmark offline inference throughput."
msgstr ""
"- `latency`：基准测试单批次请求的延迟。\n"
"- `serve`：基准测试在线服务吞吐量。\n"
"- `throughput`：基准测试离线推理吞吐量。"

msgid ""
"The performance evaluation must be conducted in an online mode. Take the "
"`serve` as an example. Run the code as follows."
msgstr "性能评估必须以在线模式进行。以 `serve` 为例，运行代码如下。"

msgid ""
"After about several minutes, you can get the performance evaluation result."
msgstr "大约几分钟后，您将获得性能评估结果。"

msgid "## 9 Performance Tuning"
msgstr "## 9 性能调优"

msgid "### 9.1 Recommended Configurations"
msgstr "### 9.1 推荐配置"

msgid ""
"> **Note**: The following configurations are validated in specific test "
"environments and are for reference only. The optimal configuration depends "
"on factors such as maximum input/output length, prefix cache hit rate, "
"precision requirements, and deployment machine ratios. It is recommended to "
"refer to Section 9.2 for tuning based on actual conditions."
msgstr ""
"> "
"**注意**：以下配置在特定测试环境中验证，仅供参考。最佳配置取决于最大输入/输出长度、前缀缓存命中率、精度要求和部署机器比例等因素。建议参考第9.2节根据实际情况进行调优。"

msgid "#### Table 1: Scenario Overview"
msgstr "#### 表1：场景概览"

msgid ""
"|Scenario|Deployment Mode|*Total NPUs|Weight Version|Key Considerations|\n"
"|--------|---------------|-----------|--------------|------------------|\n"
"|High Throughput<br>(16K context)|Single-Node Mixed|1 (A3)|Qwen3-VL-8B-Instruct|Use tp2 for high-resolution text inputs|\n"
"|Long Context<br>(128K, no prefix cache)|Single-Node Mixed|1 (A3)|Qwen3-VL-8B-Instruct|tp2 for high-resolution text inputs|\n"
"|Long Context<br>(128K, with prefix cache)|Single-Node Mixed|1 (A3)|Qwen3-VL-8B-Instruct|tp2 for high-resolution text inputs|\n"
"|Multimodal<br>(1080P)|Single-Node Mixed|1 (A3)|Qwen3-VL-8B-Instruct|tp2 for high-resolution visual inputs|"
msgstr ""
"|场景|部署模式|*总NPU数|权重版本|关键考量|\n"
"|--------|---------------|-----------|--------------|------------------|\n"
"|高吞吐<br>(16K上下文)|单节点混合|1 (A3)|Qwen3-VL-8B-Instruct|高分辨率文本输入使用tp2|\n"
"|长上下文<br>(128K，无前缀缓存)|单节点混合|1 (A3)|Qwen3-VL-8B-Instruct|高分辨率文本输入使用tp2|\n"
"|长上下文<br>(128K，有前缀缓存)|单节点混合|1 (A3)|Qwen3-VL-8B-Instruct|高分辨率文本输入使用tp2|\n"
"|多模态<br>(1080P)|单节点混合|1 (A3)|Qwen3-VL-8B-Instruct|高分辨率视觉输入使用tp2|"

msgid ""
"> `*Total NPUs` indicates the total number of NPUs used across all nodes. 1 "
"node = 1 Atlas 800 A3 server (64G × 16 NPUs)."
msgstr "> `*总NPU数` 表示所有节点使用的NPU总数。1个节点 = 1台Atlas 800 A3服务器（64G × 16 NPU）。"

msgid "#### Table 2: Detailed Node Configuration"
msgstr "#### 表2：详细节点配置"

msgid ""
"|Scenario|Configuration|NPUs|TP|DP|Max Model Len|MTP Speculation Num|Weight Version|\n"
"|--------|-------------|-----|--|--|-------------------|--------------------|---|\n"
"|High Throughput / Low Latency (16K)|Server / Single Machine|1|1|1|~16K|3|Qwen3-VL-8B-Instruct|\n"
"|Long Context (128K, no cache)|Server / Single Machine|1|1|1|128K|3|Qwen3-VL-8B-Instruct|\n"
"|Long Context (128K, with cache)|Server / Single Machine|1|1|1|128K|3|Qwen3-VL-8B-Instruct|\n"
"|Multimodal (1080P)|Server / Single Machine|1|1|1|~16K|3|Qwen3-VL-8B-Instruct|"
msgstr ""
"|场景|配置|NPU数|TP|DP|最大模型长度|MTP推测数量|权重版本|\n"
"|--------|-------------|-----|--|--|-------------------|--------------------|---|\n"
"|高吞吐/低延迟 (16K)|服务器/单机|1|1|1|~16K|3|Qwen3-VL-8B-Instruct|\n"
"|长上下文 (128K，无缓存)|服务器/单机|1|1|1|128K|3|Qwen3-VL-8B-Instruct|\n"
"|长上下文 (128K，有缓存)|服务器/单机|1|1|1|128K|3|Qwen3-VL-8B-Instruct|\n"
"|多模态 (1080P)|服务器/单机|1|1|1|~16K|3|Qwen3-VL-8B-Instruct|"

msgid ""
"> For complete startup commands and parameter descriptions, please refer to "
"the deployment examples in [Chapter 5](#5-online-service-deployment)."
msgstr "> 完整的启动命令和参数说明请参考[第5章](#5-在线服务部署)中的部署示例。"

msgid ""
"**Notice:**\n"
"`max-model-len` and `max-num-seqs` need to be set according to the actual usage scenario. For other settings, please refer to the **[Deployment](#5-online-service-deployment)** chapter."
msgstr ""
"**注意：**\n"
"`max-model-len` 和 `max-num-seqs` 需要根据实际使用场景设置。其他设置请参考 **[部署](#5-在线服务部署)** 章节。"

